times, people normally

00:03:38.070 --> 00:03:43.140 align:middle line:84%
went through initiation by
joining a particular initiation

00:03:43.140 --> 00:03:45.775 align:middle line:84%
group, often a closed
group, and you'd

00:03:45.775 --> 00:03:48.025 align:middle line:84%
be a part of that one group
for the rest of your life.

00:03:48.025 --> 00:03:48.540 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:50.880 align:middle line:84%
>> GILBERT: And so you would
go very deep in that one

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:53.100 align:middle line:84%
tradition, but you wouldn't
learn things from other

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:54.660 align:middle line:90%
perspectives necessarily.

00:03:54.660 --> 00:03:57.960 align:middle line:84%
And you would have a particular
teacher or a guru who really

00:03:57.960 --> 00:04:00.090 align:middle line:90%
guided the entire process.

00:04:00.090 --> 00:04:02.070 align:middle line:84%
There's been a huge
change in the last couple

00:04:02.070 --> 00:04:03.930 align:middle line:90%
of hundred years.

00:04:03.930 --> 00:04:06.390 align:middle line:84%
Part of it was the
Scientific Revolution

00:04:06.390 --> 00:04:09.780 align:middle line:84%
where the old religions
began to die to some extent

00:04:09.780 --> 00:04:11.700 align:middle line:84%
and people became
more independent

00:04:11.700 --> 00:04:13.500 align:middle line:90%
in their spiritual search.

00:04:13.500 --> 00:04:15.630 align:middle line:84%
But today there's
developed a kind

00:04:15.630 --> 00:04:19.110 align:middle line:84%
of independent
initiatory process

00:04:19.110 --> 00:04:21.000 align:middle line:84%
that people are
voting with their feet

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:22.540 align:middle line:90%
to do all over the world.

00:04:22.540 --> 00:04:24.570 align:middle line:84%
So now millions upon
millions of people

00:04:24.570 --> 00:04:27.540 align:middle line:84%
do not say that they have one
particular tradition or one

00:04:27.540 --> 00:04:29.850 align:middle line:84%
particular teacher,
but rather, they're

00:04:29.850 --> 00:04:32.580 align:middle line:84%
gathering information
from everywhere,

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:34.608 align:middle line:84%
and that's really what
I think Gaia is about.

00:04:34.608 --> 00:04:36.150 align:middle line:84%
To gather information
from everywhere

00:04:36.150 --> 00:04:38.580 align:middle line:84%
and put it into a
useful system that

00:04:38.580 --> 00:04:41.910 align:middle line:90%
works for whatever they need.

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:48.030 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's in a really, I
think, well-considered process.

00:04:48.030 --> 00:04:51.570 align:middle line:84%
Whereas a lot of times what
people tend to do also is

00:04:51.570 --> 00:04:53.100 align:middle line:84%
