cherry-pick a little

00:04:53.100 --> 00:04:54.183 align:middle line:90%
of this, a little of that.

00:04:54.183 --> 00:04:57.100 align:middle line:84%
Cobble something together that
already reflects who they are.

00:04:57.100 --> 00:04:57.900 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: Right.

00:04:57.900 --> 00:05:00.480 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And that's where
it starts breaking down,

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:03.840 align:middle line:84%
and millions of
people do that, too.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:05.280 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: Right, absolutely.

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:08.280 align:middle line:84%
If you look at the work from the
European Rosicrucians, people

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:11.760 align:middle line:84%
like Rudolf Steiner, they
really emphasize this concept

00:05:11.760 --> 00:05:14.730 align:middle line:84%
that in modern times,
self-initiation

00:05:14.730 --> 00:05:16.960 align:middle line:84%
is a major part of
spiritual development.

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:17.760 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:20.093 align:middle line:84%
>> GILBERT: Because we are
able to choose and learn from

00:05:20.093 --> 00:05:23.270 align:middle line:84%
so many different
traditions and teachers.

00:05:23.270 --> 00:05:29.300 align:middle line:84%
But this requires that we
have a very keen intelligence

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:31.100 align:middle line:84%
to work through a
lot of information.

00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:33.930 align:middle line:84%
We have to be very proactive
and put it together

00:05:33.930 --> 00:05:37.190 align:middle line:84%
so the different pieces actually
form a coherent whole that

00:05:37.190 --> 00:05:39.770 align:middle line:84%
creates something in our
own personal development

00:05:39.770 --> 00:05:42.600 align:middle line:84%
that actually leads us to
where we need to get to.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:44.810 align:middle line:84%
And as part of
that understanding

00:05:44.810 --> 00:05:47.840 align:middle line:84%
of the context we're
working in, discernment

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:49.610 align:middle line:84%
is the absolute
foundation of everything.

00:05:49.610 --> 00:05:51.860 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Absolutely, and
that's what we appear to be

00:05:51.860 --> 00:05:54.680 align:middle line:84%
lacking right now across
the board as a species.

00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:57.440 align:middle line:84%
And that's one of the
things about Steiner's work

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:58.790 align:middle line:90%
that was so beautiful.

00:05:58.790 --> 00:06:02.450 align:middle line:84%
Is it was cohesive,
even more so than I

00:06:02.450 --> 00:06:04.670 align:middle line:84%
think a lot of the
ancient traditions,

00:06:04.670 --> 00:06:07.100 align:middle line:84%
which brought in a
lot of information.

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:10.430 align:middle line:84%
I call a Hermetic education
a proper education because it

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:12.200 align:middle line:90%
spans everything, from--

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:15.300 align:middle line:84%
in all of the sciences
to art to poetry

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:18.080 align:middle line:84%
to color and light
and the cosmos.

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:19.760 align:middle line:90%
That's a proper education.

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:22.130 align:middle line:84%
But it is like a
liberal arts education

00:06:22.130 --> 00:06:25.400 align:middle line:84%
that's deeply
spiritual, whereas what

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:29.600 align:middle line:84%
he was doing with anthroposophy
was very, very focused

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:32.060 align:middle line:84%
around a type of
human development

00:06:32.060 --> 00:06:34.162 align:middle line:84%
that you could kind of
get your mind around.

00:06:34.162 --> 00:06:35.120 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: Absolutely.

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:35.920 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:39.530 align:middle line:84%
>> GILBERT: And so to have
true freedom in our spiritual

00:06:39.530 --> 00:06:42.590 align:middle line:84%
development, I think that's only
possible if we have sufficient

00:06:42.590 --> 00:06:43.760 align:middle line:90%
contextual knowledge.

00:06:43.760 --> 00:06:44.120 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:45.800 align:middle line:84%
>> GILBERT: If you don't
have contextual knowledge,

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:48.008 align:middle line:84%
you don't have enough
information to make an informed

00:06:48.008 --> 00:06:50.270 align:middle line:84%
choice, and then
there's no freedom.

00:06:50.270 --> 00:06:52.700 align:middle line:84%
And so to have the
discernment, then,

00:06:52.700 --> 00:06:56.750 align:middle line:84%
to be able to choose what
is the best pathway or what,

00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:58.460 align:middle line:84%
in my limited amount
of time and energy

00:06:58.460 --> 00:07:01.910 align:middle line:84%
that any person has, where do
I want to focus my attention

00:07:01.910 --> 00:07:05.480 align:middle line:84%
to develop my core structure
to the level that's going to be

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:06.980 align:middle line:90%
the most important for me?

00:07:06.980 --> 00:07:10.280 align:middle line:84%
And from my perspective, to
go beyond the present lifetime

00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:14.000 align:middle line:84%
something that becomes the
core of our development

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:15.350 align:middle line:90%
that we can keep?

00:07:15.350 --> 00:07:18.260 align:middle line:84%
Because I believe
that after we die,

00:07:18.260 --> 00:07:21.470 align:middle line:84%
we lose all the superficial
aspects, but what we keep

00:07:21.470 --> 00:07:23.235 align:middle line:84%
is the core structure
of the subtle bodies

00:07:23.235 --> 00:07:24.110 align:middle line:90%
in the consciousness.

00:07:24.110 --> 00:07:24.590 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:07:24.590 --> 00:07:25.840 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: And that moves on.

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.500 align:middle line:84%
So if we use our
lifetimes properly,

00:07:28.500 --> 00:07:30.320 align:middle line:84%
we can really structure
the subtle bodies

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:32.600 align:middle line:84%
so that we can take that
through the gate of death

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:35.273 align:middle line:84%
and keep moving through a
true initiatory process.

00:07:35.273 --> 00:07:36.440 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: You are so right.

00:07:36.440 --> 00:07:38.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm so glad you're so
articulate in the way you

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:39.800 align:middle line:90%
state all of this.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:41.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm really very
appreciative of your saying

