School of Hard Knocks.

00:08:26.330 --> 00:08:27.620 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You can
stumble through it.

00:08:27.620 --> 00:08:28.662 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: That's right.

00:08:28.662 --> 00:08:31.160 align:middle line:84%
And you're better off choosing
the School of Skillful Means

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:33.368 align:middle line:84%
