biological, chemical warfare

00:11:02.500 --> 00:11:04.545 align:middle line:90%
defense and survival.

00:11:04.545 --> 00:11:06.670 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Did you have
any schooling or background

00:11:06.670 --> 00:11:06.970 align:middle line:90%
in this?

00:11:06.970 --> 00:11:08.860 align:middle line:84%
