00:11:32.832 --> 00:11:34.040 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: And none for life.

00:11:34.040 --> 00:11:35.380 align:middle line:90%
>> GILBERT: Exactly.

00:11:35.380 --> 00:11:37.960 align:middle line:84%
And so it's a fairly
sobering field

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:42.070 align:middle line:84%
to be involved in nuclear,
biological, chemical warfare.

00:11:42.070 --> 00:11:46.640 align:middle line:84%
This is basically finding, how
