00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:51.670 align:middle line:84%
So again, it's a
very sobering field

00:11:51.670 --> 00:11:54.100 align:middle line:90%
to be a part of as a young man.

00:11:54.100 --> 00:11:58.210 align:middle line:84%
But it also was something that
awakened in me the importance

00:11:58.210 --> 00:12:01.000 align:middle line:84%
of understanding how do we
develop in a positive sense

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:02.980 align:middle line:84%
to be able to
counterbalance this?

00:12:02.980 --> 00:12:05.680 align:middle line:84%
But also held within
