And so it's an
implosive movement.

00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:39.330 align:middle line:84%
It's going from
periphery to center.

00:29:39.330 --> 00:29:42.690 align:middle line:84%
And in doing that, you're moving
into higher consciousness.

00:29:42.690 --> 00:29:44.610 align:middle line:90%
You're moving into other worlds.

00:29:44.610 --> 00:29:49.500 align:middle line:84%
That's the method to be able to
navigate through higher realms.

