an organ of perception

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:58.230 align:middle line:84%
of non-physical realities
by going into the center,

00:29:58.230 --> 00:30:00.130 align:middle line:90%
to the inner world.

00:30:00.130 --> 00:30:03.240 align:middle line:84%
And so some traditions
teach only that aspect.

00:30:03.240 --> 00:30:06.010 align:middle line:84%
Other traditions teach
only the next step of it,

00:30:06.010 --> 00:30:08.610 align:middle line:84%
which is once you go all
the way into that center

00:30:08.610 --> 00:30:11.910 align:middle line:84%
