00:31:59.630 --> 00:32:01.820 align:middle line:84%
And so your energetic
field expands,

00:32:01.820 --> 00:32:04.010 align:middle line:84%
and the vibrational qualities
from that expansion,

00:32:04.010 --> 00:32:05.990 align:middle line:84%
like the gold sphere
around the head,

00:32:05.990 --> 00:32:08.210 align:middle line:84%
then begins to
literally illuminate

00:32:08.210 --> 00:32:10.530 align:middle line:84%
our thoughts and
our consciousness.

00:32:10.530 --> 00:32:12.350 align:middle line:10%
So we need to have
an understanding

00:32:12.350 --> 00:32:13.630 align:middle line:10%
