up the original divine

00:33:10.640 --> 00:33:14.630 align:middle line:84%
fire, of course, in the
tailbone and the sacrum.

00:33:14.630 --> 00:33:18.350 align:middle line:84%
And then you're sending
the energy up the spine

00:33:18.350 --> 00:33:21.260 align:middle line:84%
and also activating the
ida-pingala channels

00:33:21.260 --> 00:33:26.270 align:middle line:84%
as it's going up and conducing
through the different chakras

00:33:26.270 --> 00:33:29.270 align:middle line:84%
until you can then reach the
points in the head to get

00:33:29.270 --> 00:33:31.230 align:middle line:90%
a full illumination process.

00:33:31.230 --> 00:33:34.610 align:middle line:84%
So you have below-upwards
with Kundalini activation

00:33:34.610 --> 00:33:36.830 align:middle line:90%
as one possible method.

00:33:36.830 --> 00:33:40.370 align:middle line:84%
Then later Western traditions
tended to focus on a top-down

00:33:40.370 --> 00:33:43.580 align:middle line:84%
method, and that was symbolized
in the Christian ministries

00:33:43.580 --> 00:33:44.570 align:middle line:90%
as showing--

00:33:44.570 --> 00:33:47.060 align:middle line:84%
and you see this in very
ancient illustrations where

00:33:47.060 --> 00:33:49.490 align:middle line:84%
there is a pillar of
light around Jesus

00:33:49.490 --> 00:33:51.770 align:middle line:84%
at the time of the
baptism in the Jordan.

00:33:51.770 --> 00:33:54.080 align:middle line:84%
And there's the dove of the
Holy Spirit descending down

00:33:54.080 --> 00:33:56.210 align:middle line:90%
