00:34:40.679 --> 00:34:43.250 align:middle line:84%
And then that creates
an organizing center

00:34:43.250 --> 00:34:45.020 align:middle line:84%
for the rest of
the energy system.

00:34:45.020 --> 00:34:46.880 align:middle line:84%
And they explain that
until you have that,

00:34:46.880 --> 00:34:49.130 align:middle line:84%
