an organizing center

00:34:49.130 --> 00:34:50.989 align:middle line:84%
to keep all the
other activations

00:34:50.989 --> 00:34:52.469 align:middle line:90%
in the right balance.

00:34:52.469 --> 00:34:54.739 align:middle line:84%
And so they do it
from center-outward.

00:34:54.739 --> 00:34:56.870 align:middle line:84%
